    dc:creator "Suárez-Morales, Eduardo; Fuentes-Reinés, Juan M." ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Mesochra (Copepoda: Harpacticoida: Canthocamptidae) from a coastal system of northern Colombia with a key to the American species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002393>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002399>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002395>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002397> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002393>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Mesochra huysi sp. nov., adult female from Colombia: (A) habitus, dorsal view; (B) same, lateral view; (C) antennule; (D) genital field and sixth legs, ventral view; (E) anal operculum, dorsal view. Scale bars: A, B = 100 μm, C–E = 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002393/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002399>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Mesochra huysi sp. nov., adult male from Colombia: (A) antennule; (B) leg 3 showing flame-shaped element (arrowed) and remarkably large spinules on second exopodal segment (double arrow); (C) P5; (D) ornamentation of urosome and caudal rami, ventral view. Adult female, (E) P5 showing setal nomenclature (Huys et al. 1996); F. ornamentation of urosome and armature of caudal rami, ventral view. Scale bars: A–C, E = 20 μm, D, F = 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002395>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Mesochra huysi sp. nov., adult female from Colombia: (A) antenna; (B) mandibular palp; (C) maxillule; (D) maxilla; (E) maxilliped. Scale bars: A, D, E = 20 μm, B, C = 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002397>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Mesochra huysi sp. nov., adult female from Colombia: (A) leg 1; (B) leg 2; (C) leg 3; (D) leg 4. Scale bars: 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002397/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

